name: Biological Daughter
definition: A female progeny with genetic makeup inherited from the parent.

name: Biological Son
definition: A male progeny with genetic makeup inherited from the parent.

name: Biological Maternal Grandfather
definition: A male relative who is the biological father of the biological mother.

name: Biological Paternal Grandfather
definition: A male relative who is the biological father of the biological father.

name: Biological Paternal Grandmother
definition: A female relative who is the biological mother of the biological father.

name: Biological Maternal Grandmother
definition: A female relative who is the biological mother of the biological mother.

name: Biological Maternal Cousin
definition: A relative who is the offspring of a sibling of the biological mother and thus sharing a common ancestor.

name: Biological Paternal Cousin
definition: A relative who is the offspring of a sibling of the biological father and thus sharing a common ancestor.

name: Biological Paternal Aunt
definition: A female relative who is a sibling of the biological father, and who both share a common ancestor.

name: Biological Maternal Aunt
definition: A female relative who is a sibling of the biological mother, and who both share a common ancestor.

name: Biological Father
definition: A male who contributes to the genetic makeup of his offspring through the fertilization of an ovum by his sperm.

name: Biological Mother
definition: A female who contributes to the genetic makeup of her offspring from the fertilization of her ovum.

name: Half-brother with Father as Common Parent
definition: A male sibling who shares the genetic makeup inherited from only the biological father.

name: Half-sister with Father as Common Parent
definition: A female sibling who shares the genetic makeup inherited from only the biological father.

name: Half-brother with Mother as Common Parent
definition: A male sibling who shares the genetic makeup inherited from only the biological mother.

name: Half-sister with Mother as Common Parent
definition: A female sibling who shares the genetic makeup inherited from only the biological mother.

name: Fraternal Twin Brother
definition: A male full sibling that developed from a separately fertilized ova during the same pregnancy.

name: Fraternal Twin Sister
definition: A female full sibling that developed from a separately fertilized ova during the same pregnancy.

name: Identical Twin Brother
definition: A male full sibling that developed from a shared ovum.

name: Identical Twin Sister
definition: A female full sibling that developed from a shared ovum.

name: Full Brother
definition: A male who shares with his sibling the genetic makeup inherited from both of the biological parents.

name: Full Sister
definition: A female who shares with her sibling the genetic makeup inherited from both of the biological parents.

name: Grandson
definition: A male grandchild.

name: Granddaughter
definition: A female grandchild.

name: Biological Maternal Uncle
definition: A male relative who is a sibling of the biological mother, and who both share a common ancestor.

name: Biological Paternal Uncle
definition: A male relative who is a sibling of the biological father, and who both share a common ancestor.

name: Niece
definition: A daughter of your brother or sister.

name: Nephew
definition: A son of your brother or sister.

name: Ancestor
definition: Someone from whom you are descended (but usually more remote than a grandparent).

name: Maternal First Cousin Once Removed
definition: A child of one's first cousin who is related by lineage through the mother's side of the family.

name: Paternal First Cousin Once Removed
definition: A child of one's first cousin who is related by lineage through the father's side of the family.

name: Descendent
definition: Someone deriving or descending from an ancestor.

name: Great Grandchild
definition: A child of one's grandchild.

name: Maternal Great Grandparent
definition: A parent of one's maternal grandparent.

name: Paternal Great Grandparent
definition: A parent of one's paternal grandparent.

name: Great Nephew
definition: A male child of one's niece or nephew.

name: Great Niece
definition: A female child of one's niece or nephew.

name: Maternal Great Aunt
definition: The aunt of one's mother.

name: Maternal Great Uncle
definition: The uncle of one's mother.

name: Paternal Great Aunt
definition: The aunt of one's father.

name: Paternal Great Uncle
definition: The uncle of one's father.
